metadata.name: My Favorite NFT Album #1
metadata.description:
### Show off your favorite NFTs with this beautiful 8.5 Inch Square NFT Album!
  With a minimum of 24 and a maximun of 40 pages of awesomeness you can display **up to a 100** of your NFTs, **no matter which chain they are on!**
  So purchase your NFT Album, pick your favorite theme, submit the list of your NFTs you want to showcase, and we will send you layouts for approval.
 Once the design is done we will update your album and date stamp it, **forever recording your favorite NFTs at that moment in time.** Your IRL Hard Cover NFT Album will be delivered to you within 3-4 weeks if you are in the US or Canada. For the rest of the world, our team will give you Delivery timelines and cost (If any) once they confirmed your address.
